      <h3>HTML Paragraph</h3>
      <div>
         <p>HTML Paragraph is used to display a section block of text. Content of paragraph tag is displayed in a new block. Browser adds a new line before and after a paragraph.
            Some margine is also added on the top and bottom of a paragraph. HTML paragraph is defined by
             <span class="blue"><</span><span class="blue"></span><span class="red-brown">p</span><span class="blue">></span> <span class="blue"><</span><span class="blue">/</span><span class="red-brown">p</span><span class="blue">></span> element.   
         </p>
      </div>

